timelineItems.desc:
D.C. United center back pair Bobby Boswell and Steve Birnbaum interview each other at the MLSsoccer.com studios to get to know each other a little better.

Heineken Rivalry Week: Watch D.C United take on rivals New York Red Bulls Sunday, August 30th at 7pm ET on Fox Sports 1.
